# Testing

Always use `yarn test` to run the test suite. Never use `npx jest` or `npm test`.

```bash
# ✅ GOOD
yarn test

# ❌ BAD
npx jest
npm test
npx jest --testPathPattern="..."
```

When running a subset of tests, pass args through yarn:

```bash
yarn test --testPathPattern="some-pattern"
```
